For more detailed installation instructions, please refere to the document 
section on http://github.com/biointec/blstools.

Dependencies
============

 - CMake version 2.6 or higher
 - C++ compiler with C++11 support
 - BLAS (Basic Linear Algebra Subroutines)

Compilation instructions
========================

# compilation instructions:

 > mkdir build
 > cd build
 > cmake ..
 > make

# optionally:

 > make install

